
This is test web project represents a web application created use Python and Django.
It's display a list of books(each book have fields: "name", "description", "author"), like library and also you can add book into the list or commenting existing books.
The main page display all list, the name of book is link to detail books view. Detail view include comments list and comment form with sending comment without refresh page.
Welcome!

